{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"摘要","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Digest","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>摘要</strong>是一个由 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptographic_hash_function\">散列函数 <small>(en-US)</small></a> 从完整的消息生成的小的值。理想情况下，摘要是可快速计算、不可逆且不可预测的，因此可用于表明是否有人篡改了给定的消息。</p>\n<p>摘要可用于执行多种任务：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>非加密类应用（例如：哈希表的索引、用于检测重复数据或唯一标识文件的指纹）</li>\n  <li>验证消息完整性（被篡改的消息具有不同的散列值）</li>\n  <li>生成伪随机数</li>\n  <li>生成<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Key\">密钥</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>为应用选择合适的散列函数以避免冲突和可预测至关重要。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptographic_hash_function\">密码散列函数 <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li>维基百科上的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptographic_hash_function\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">密码散列函数</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"摘要是一个由 散列函数 (en-US) 从完整的消息生成的小的值。理想情况下，摘要是可快速计算、不可逆且不可预测的，因此可用于表明是否有人篡改了给定的消息。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Digest","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Condensé","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Digest","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/digest","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/digest/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Digest","title":"摘要"}],"pageTitle":"摘要 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}